     H            Y/
     F***************************************************
     F*   WASHER LIST TO  PC
     F*                                                 *
     F***************************************************
     FGDGPW53 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     F                                              KINFDS @INFDS
     FFCEPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FMCENP13 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAKBPL08 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAAMPL11 IF  E           K        DISK
     FGDGWP53 O   E                    DISK
      *------------------------------------------------------------
     E                    KB         15  3               MACHINE
     E                    KO         15  3               PROCESS
     E                    MC         50  3
      *------------------------------------------------------------
     I@INFDS      DS
     I                                    B 378 3790@@REC
     I            DS
     I                                        1  45 KB
     I                                        1   3 CKKB01
     I                                        4   6 CKKB02
     I                                        7   9 CKKB03
     I                                       10  12 CKKB04
     I                                       13  15 CKKB05
     I                                       16  18 CKKB06
     I                                       19  21 CKKB07
     I                                       22  24 CKKB08
